It could be worse. He could be VU'd to look like a 40 years hag old with a shit ton of failed plastic surgery. {{champion:114}} 

On a serious note, my condolences for the death of your main. I too have been through this with Fiora and I'm still struggling with the loss.

Goes to show no matter how much you support Riot with all these purchases of champs and skins that at the end of the day they really don't give a shit about the playerbase. You know, the people that fucking allow them to receive a check every two motherfucking weeks.
